summary: a statement to branch conditionally to a paragraph within a program
format: [47,] >> - "IF" - BooleanExpression - "THEN" -2 Statement - ^7 - #1 -13 #2 -6 >< &1 \2 "ELSE" -2 Statement - ^7 /2 &2 \ "END" /
remarks: <ul>
	an <code>END</code>-less <code>IF</code> is terminated at the end of the sentence (by <code>.</code>)
</ul>
